title: Jake Owen Performs In Studio And Talks Acting + Bobby Talks With A Woman Who Married Herself + Fun Fact Friday-Off: Raymundo vs. Scuba Steve
itunes:title: Jake Owen Performs In Studio And Talks Acting + Bobby Talks With A Woman Who Married Herself + Fun Fact Friday-Off: Raymundo vs. Scuba Steve
description:
Jake Owen stops by who is one of our favorite guests. He performs a few of his hits for us including his now 9th No. 1 “Made For You”. Bobby talks to a woman who married herself…which sounds crazy but we find is actually pretty inspiring. We do our Fun Fact Friday Faceoff between Raymundo and Scuba Steve to see who can bring the 5 most fun facts.
